	   <tr><td colspan=2>One additional note based on personal experience:<br><br>Vah Shir are a large race.&nbsp;&nbsp;That means you don't always fit in the doorway.  Since bards are a plate armor class the extra STR a Vah Shir gets helps.<br><br>Recursion is right about STA. But since I hit level 23 I do mostly instrument twisting instead of melee.  So, I don't have much of a fatique issue.  I guess it depends on how you play the class.  Once thing about bards - your play strategy can change drastically at every new level.  <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
