	   <tr><td colspan=2>The size DOES NOT MATTER for things as stupid as fitting in a doorway.<br><br>There really isn't a good race or bad race for bards.&nbsp;&nbsp;Not even really better or worse.  i like vah shir cause it breaks away from the mainstream of all half elvenbards.  Which I hear are the best stat wise, which is total crap, because the bard can be played many different ways.  it just depends on your play style.  And Stamina is one of the most important points for a bard.  Any kind of kiting, you want to be able to last longer.<br><br>My two cents.  Drop me a tell on 7th hammer if you have more questions.<br>&nbsp;<br>Eclyptic Starsonata<br>[65(14) Maestro]<br>Phearmydot Andlargepoon<br>[59(3) Luminary]625388<br>Nandar Stormstrider<br>[61(13) Hierophant]</td></tr>
