	   <tr><td colspan=2>The only thing about AGI is that it seems to convert 4 AGI=1 AC.&nbsp;&nbsp;With STA you get more like 1 STA=4 HP at higher levels (its all level dependent, too).  Best to work on that STA.  DEX is more important at lower levels for skill ups. Once you hit your skill caps its not as important unless you have weapons with procs.  Recently confirmed info shows that CHA can make a difference on whether or not a failed mezz attempt results in aggro.  It also has a small bearing on charm success rates, I have noticed. So, get the STA up, get HP, get AC and get resist gear. <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
